{
  "page": "Stonecrab Cay",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Stonecrab Cay</b> is a small isle off the coast of the <a href=\"/index.php/Arbor\" title=\"Arbor\">Arbor</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Stonecrab_Cay&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Feast_for_Crows\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Stonecrab_Cay&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Feast for Crows\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Stonecrab Cay is attacked and conquered by the <a href=\"/index.php/Ironborn\" title=\"Ironborn\">ironborn</a>, along with the <a href=\"/index.php/Isle_of_Pigs\" title=\"Isle of Pigs\">Isle of Pigs</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Mermaid%27s_Palace\" title=\"Mermaid&#39;s Palace\">Mermaid's Palace</a>. It is now used as one of their bases.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Stonecrab_Cay&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Ref